tternsApplied: comma-separated patterns used (e.g. \"repository pattern, debounce, memoization\")\n\n2. Verify: `npx tsc --noEmit` (fix any type errors)\n\nBegin implementation now."}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"2fae1135-03d8-419c-8f90-568496f0fed8","uuid":"b12a258b-a0a3-4189-9a6f-12d51ae16c76","timestamp":"2026-03-19T08:15:53.803Z","isSynthetic":true}
